title: Did U.S. Rep. Ocasio-Cortez Graduate Cum Laude from Boston University?
subtitle: While "bartender" may be the most frequently mentioned part of her résumé, the congresswoman has quite a few other accomplishments to her name.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez graduated cum laude from Boston University's College of Arts and Sciences in 2011.
